(10, 'B000FGD2SQ', 'http://www.amazon.com/Open-Air-Cinema-16-feet-Projector/dp/B000FGD2SQ%3FSubscriptionId%3DAKIAI3XM53IGZRPXET5Q%26tag%3Dgalgome-20%26linkCode%3Dxm2%26camp%3D2025%26creative%3D165953%26creativeASIN%3DB000FGD2SQ', 'Open Air Cinema 16-feet Outdoor Home Projector Screen', 'Open Air Home Screens rip the roof off the home theater and takes it outside. This is no cheap, sagging, inflatable screen. Set up is a snap. Simply attach the quiet air blower to inflate the screen and tie down to twist stakes.\nThe Open Air Home Screen''s intelligent design provides optimum tension for the projection surface without the work of tying, clipping or zipping on a projection surface.', 1185.99, 80193, 2, '1475424583', '1342372375', 'http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/41OSC-6gjcL.jpg'),
(11, 'B001M5U5AC', 'http://www.amazon.com/Logitech-Harmony-Universal-Discontinued-Manufacturer/dp/B001M5U5AC%3FSubscriptionId%3DAKIAI3XM53IGZRPXET5Q%26tag%3Dgalgome-20%26linkCode%3Dxm2%26camp%3D2025%26creative%3D165953%26creativeASIN%3DB001M5U5AC', 'Logitech Harmony 1100 Universal Remote with Color Touch Screen (Discontinued by Manufacturer)', 'The Logitech Harmony 1100 gives you powerful home-entertainment control through a customizable, 3.5-inch full-color touch screen. Controls are easy to access and are backlit, so you can easily find them in the dark. One-touch, activity-based controls turn on the right devices in the right order with a single command. RF wireless capability lets you control devices without direct line-of-sight, so you can keep components in a closed cabinet or even another room (requires Logitech Harmony RF Extender, sold separately). The on-screen commands are customizable, so you get the commands you want, when you want them. The Harmony 1100 supports more than 5000 brands and over 225,000 devices.', 399.99, 25850, 2, '1472837318', '1342372379', 'http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/81XMpnbuVRL.jpg'),
